org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.jobhistory

接口 HistoryEvent

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AMStartedEvent, JobFinishedEvent, JobInfoChangeEvent, JobInitedEvent, JobPriorityChangeEvent, JobQueueChangeEvent, JobStatusChangedEvent, JobSubmittedEvent, JobUnsuccessfulCompletionEvent, MapAttemptFinishedEvent, NormalizedResourceEvent, ReduceAttemptFinishedEvent, TaskAttemptFinishedEvent, TaskAttemptStartedEvent, TaskAttemptUnsuccessfulCompletionEvent, TaskFailedEvent, TaskFinishedEvent, TaskStartedEvent, TaskUpdatedEvent

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
@InterfaceStability.Unstable
public interface HistoryEvent
    Interface for event wrapper classes. Implementations each wrap an Avro-generated class, adding constructors and accessor methods.
